Check if a test exists by name. Useful if a test may be
optionally available.

```jinja
{% if 'loud' is test %}
    {% if value is loud %}
        {{ value|upper }}
    {% else %}
        {{ value|lower }}
    {% endif %}
{% else %}
    {{ value }}
{% endif %}
```

